<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #10B981; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .points-box { background-color: #ECFDF5; color: #065F46; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Attendance Verified!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
      <p>Thank you for attending <strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong>.</p>
      <p>Your participation helps us build a better community.</p>
      
      <div class="points-box">
        Points Earned: +{{pointsEarned}}
      </div>

      <p>Your total points: {{totalPoints}}</p>
      <p>Keep up the great work!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} SevaSetu. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
